data.description:
Photos coming soon! 

This home has a lot of offer! From two oversized bedrooms, a private fenced in back yard with a deck, to easy to maintain tile flooring on the main floor. As soon as you walk in, you'll be greeted with the large living room with wood beams, newer ceramic tile, and dining room right around the corner that leads out to the deck in the back yard. Complete with an updated kitchen with gorgeous cabinets and backsplash. With a park close by too! Come see for yourself and make this home yours!
